[As stated in the full report, in order to have an effective and safe simulation exercise, a strategy must be developed for clear communication with the community leaders, the public, and the media, so that panic does not ensue following dissemination of misinformation. The WHO has guidelines for such exercises. See https://www.who.int/ihr/publications/WHO-WHE-CPI-2017.10/en/ - Mod.LK]

